      <title>민생회복지원금과 복지 정책: 선별 복지와 보편 복지의 관점</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1321/posts/2024-07-31-%EB%AF%BC%EC%83%9D%ED%9A%8C%EB%B3%B5%EC%A7%80%EC%9B%90%EA%B8%88%EA%B3%BC-%EB%B3%B5%EC%A7%80-%EC%A0%95%EC%B1%85-%EC%84%A0%EB%B3%84-%EB%B3%B5%EC%A7%80%EC%99%80-%EB%B3%B4%ED%8E%B8-%EB%B3%B5%EC%A7%80%EC%9D%98-%EA%B4%80%EC%A0%90/</link>
